summary: David Tennant Is Going To Host A Podcast
title: David Tennant Is Going To Host A Podcast
body:
David Tennant is getting into the podcasting world.  The actor will host “David Tennant Does A Podcast With…’ for Somethin’ Else and No Mystery Production.  The first guest on the show will be Olivia Colman, and then in the coming weeks look for stars like Jon Hamm, Whoopi Goldberg, Sir Ian McKellan, Jodie Whittaker, and more.  The podcast has also started Twitter and Instagram accounts - look for @davidtennantpod . 

(via Steve Ackerman)

summary: David Tennant has just launched his own podcast – and one of his first guests will be Doctor Who's Jodie Whittaker
title: David Tennant has just launched his own podcast – and one of his first guests will be Doctor Who's Jodie Whittaker
excerpt: Jodie Whittaker, Olivia Colman and Ian McKellen are all lined up to appear in David Tennant's new podcast
description: The actor has teased interviews with Broadchurch co-star (and now Oscar nominee) Olivia Colman, Whoopi Goldberg, Jon Hamm, Ian McKellen, Gordon Brown, Samantha Bee, Jodie Whittaker, Krysten Ritter, and his Good Omens co-star Michael Sheen.

summary: Rose: Doctor, you’re out of control.  10: I’m not out of control, I’m a law-abiding man! Rose: Oh yeah? Name one law! 10: Don’t...
body:
Rose: Doctor, you’re out of control.

10: I’m not out of control, I’m a law-abiding man!

Rose: Oh yeah? Name one law!

10: Don’t kill people?

Rose: You know what. That’s on me, I set the bar too low.
